a-src=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Speaker-SADC-600x600.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Speaker-SADC-600x600.jpg 600w\" alt=\"\" title=\"Speaker SADC\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\"  \/><\/a>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"post-entry-content\">\n\n\t<h3 class=\"entry-title\">\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/namibian-members-of-parliament-are-participating-at-the-57th-sadc-pf-plenary-assembly-in-victoria-falls-zimbabwe\/\" title=\"Namibian Members of Parliament are participating at the 57th SADC-PF Plenary Assembly in Victoria Falls, Zimbabwe.\" rel=\"bookmark\">Namibian Members of Parliament are participating at the 57th SADC-PF Plenary Assembly in Victoria Falls, Zimbabwe.<\/a>\n\t<\/h3>\n\n\t<div class=\"entry-meta\"><span class=\"category-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/home-page-slider\/\" >Home-page Slider<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/news\/\" >News<\/a><\/span><a class=\"author vcard\" href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/author\/p-dumeniparliament-na\/\" title=\"View all posts by \" rel=\"author\">By <span class=\"fn\"><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n\t<div class=\"entry-excerpt\"><p>Members who include\u00a0Hons. Longinus Iipumbu, Paula Kooper,\u00a0Paulus Mbangu, Lonia Kaishungu \u2013 Shinana and Olivia Hanghuwo are led by the Speaker of the National Assembly, Hon. Saara Kuugongelwa &#8211; Amadhila. The plenary is held under the theme\u00a0\u201cHarnessing Artificial Intelligence (AI) for effective and efficient parliamentary processes in SADC Region: Experiences, Challenges and Opportunities\u201d.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/namibian-members-of-parliament-are-participating-at-the-57th-sadc-pf-plenary-assembly-in-victoria-falls-zimbabwe\/\" class=\"post-details details-type-link\" aria-label=\"Read more about Namibian Members of Parliament are participating at the 57th SADC-PF Plenary Assembly in Victoria Falls, Zimbabwe.\" rel=\"nofollow\">Read article<i class=\"dt-icon-the7-arrow-03\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/article><article class=\"post project-odd visible post-19374 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-home-page-slider category-news category-159 category-39 description-off\" data-name=\"Palestinian Ambassador pays courtesy call on Deputy Speaker\" data-date=\"\">\n\n<div class=\"post-thumbnail-wrap\">\n\t<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/palestinian-ambassador-pays-courtesy-call-on-deputy-speaker\/\" class=\"post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg layzr-bg\" ><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"blog-thumb-lazy-load preload-me lazy-load\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D&#39;http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg&#39;%20viewBox%3D&#39;0%200%20600%20600&#39;%2F%3E\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/D-SPEaker-600x600.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/D-SPEaker-600x600.jpg 600w\" alt=\"\" title=\"D SPEaker\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\"  \/><\/a>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"post-entry-content\">\n\n\t<h3 class=\"entry-title\">\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/palestinian-ambassador-pays-courtesy-call-on-deputy-speaker\/\" title=\"Palestinian Ambassador pays courtesy call on Deputy Speaker\" rel=\"bookmark\">Palestinian Ambassador pays courtesy call on Deputy Speaker<\/a>\n\t<\/h3>\n\n\t<div class=\"entry-meta\"><span class=\"category-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/home-page-slider\/\" >Home-page Slider<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/news\/\" >News<\/a><\/span><a class=\"author vcard\" href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/author\/p-dumeniparliament-na\/\" title=\"View all posts by \" rel=\"author\">By <span class=\"fn\"><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n\t<div class=\"entry-excerpt\"><p>\u00a0Eino Vatileni Non-Resident Ambassador of the State of Palestine to Namibia, H.E. Hanan Jarrar paid a courtesy call to the National Assembly today.\u00a0\u00a0She was welcomed by the Deputy Speaker Hon.Phillipus Katamelo. The aim of the visit was to strengthen diplomatic engagements with the State of Palestine. In her address, Ambassador Jarrar provided an update on&hellip;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/palestinian-ambassador-pays-courtesy-call-on-deputy-speaker\/\" class=\"post-details details-type-link\" aria-label=\"Read more about Palestinian Ambassador pays courtesy call on Deputy Speaker\" rel=\"nofollow\">Read article<i class=\"dt-icon-the7-arrow-03\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/article><article class=\"post project-odd visible post-19346 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-home-page-slider category-news category-159 category-39 description-off\" data-name=\"Secretary of the National Assembly\" data-date=\"\">\n\n<div class=\"post-thumbnail-wrap\">\n\t<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/secretary-of-the-national-assembly\/\" class=\"post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg layzr-bg\" ><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"blog-thumb-lazy-load preload-me lazy-load\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D&#39;http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg&#39;%20viewBox%3D&#39;0%200%20600%20600&#39;%2F%3E\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/MS.Kaapanda-600x600.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/MS.Kaapanda-600x600.jpg 600w\" alt=\"\" title=\"MS.Kaapanda\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\"  \/><\/a>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"post-entry-content\">\n\n\t<h3 class=\"entry-title\">\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/secretary-of-the-national-assembly\/\" title=\"Secretary of the National Assembly\" rel=\"bookmark\">Secretary of the National Assembly<\/a>\n\t<\/h3>\n\n\t<div class=\"entry-meta\"><span class=\"category-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/home-page-slider\/\" >Home-page Slider<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/news\/\" >News<\/a><\/span><a class=\"author vcard\" href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/author\/p-dumeniparliament-na\/\" title=\"View all posts by \" rel=\"author\">By <span class=\"fn\"><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n\t<div class=\"entry-excerpt\"><\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/secretary-of-the-national-assembly\/\" class=\"post-details details-type-link\" aria-label=\"Read more about Secretary of the National Assembly\" rel=\"nofollow\">Read article<i class=\"dt-icon-the7-arrow-03\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/article><article class=\"post project-odd visible post-19214 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-home-page-slider category-news category-159 category-39 description-off\" data-name=\"MPs Urged to Uphold Accountability, Integrity\" data-date=\"\">\n\n<div class=\"post-thumbnail-wrap\">\n\t<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/mps-urged-to-uphold-accountability-integrity\/\" class=\"post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg layzr-bg\" ><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"blog-thumb-lazy-load preload-me lazy-load\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D&#39;http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg&#39;%20viewBox%3D&#39;0%200%20600%20600&#39;%2F%3E\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hon-k-600x600.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hon-k-600x600.jpg 600w\" alt=\"\" title=\"hon k\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\"  \/><\/a>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"post-entry-content\">\n\n\t<h3 class=\"entry-title\">\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/mps-urged-to-uphold-accountability-integrity\/\" title=\"MPs Urged to Uphold Accountability, Integrity\" rel=\"bookmark\">MPs Urged to Uphold Accountability, Integrity<\/a>\n\t<\/h3>\n\n\t<div class=\"entry-meta\"><span class=\"category-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/home-page-slider\/\" >Home-page Slider<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/news\/\" >News<\/a><\/span><a class=\"author vcard\" href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/author\/p-dumeniparliament-na\/\" title=\"View all posts by \" rel=\"author\">By <span class=\"fn\"><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n\t<div class=\"entry-excerpt\"><p>Zurretta Maveoro Vice Chairperson of the National Council Honourable Victoria Mbawo Kauma has called on fellow Members of Parliament to uphold the principles of accountability, transparency and integrity as they work to address challenges facing Namibians. She also called on Members to treat each other with mutual respect during debates. The Vice Chairperson made these&hellip;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/mps-urged-to-uphold-accountability-integrity\/\" class=\"post-details details-type-link\" aria-label=\"Read more about MPs Urged to Uphold Accountability, Integrity\" rel=\"nofollow\">Read article<i class=\"dt-icon-the7-arrow-03\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/article><article class=\"post project-odd hidden post-19208 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-home-page-slider category-news category-159 category-39 description-off\" data-name=\"NEW MEMBER SWEARING IN:WEDNESDAY,07 MAY 2025.\" data-date=\"\">\n\n<div class=\"post-thumbnail-wrap\">\n\t<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/new-member-swearing-inwednesday07-may-2025\/\" class=\"post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg layzr-bg\" ><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"blog-thumb-lazy-load preload-me lazy-load\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D&#39;http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg&#39;%20viewBox%3D&#39;0%200%20600%20600&#39;%2F%3E\" data-src=\