:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wamkele1-600x600.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/wamkele1-600x600.jpg 600w\" alt=\"\" title=\"wamkele1\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\"  \/><\/a>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"post-entry-content\">\n\n\t<h3 class=\"entry-title\">\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/africa-boosting-infrastruture-to-attract-investment\/\" title=\"AFRICA boosting infrastruture to attract investment.\" rel=\"bookmark\">AFRICA boosting infrastruture to attract investment.<\/a>\n\t<\/h3>\n\n\t<div class=\"entry-meta\"><span class=\"category-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/home-page-slider\/\" >Home-page Slider<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/news\/\" >News<\/a><\/span><a class=\"author vcard\" href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/author\/p-dumeniparliament-na\/\" title=\"View all posts by \" rel=\"author\">By <span class=\"fn\"><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n\t<div class=\"entry-excerpt\"><p>Story by George Sanzila Date: 13 April 2025 Antalya, Turkey &#8211; The Secretary General of the African Continental Free Trade Area (AfCFTA), Wamkele Mene says Africa has begun to fast track the development of its infrastructure alongside harmonised trade regulations to attract investment and accelerate the continent\u2019s economic development. Wamkele said this during a panel&hellip;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/africa-boosting-infrastruture-to-attract-investment\/\" class=\"post-details details-type-link\" aria-label=\"Read more about AFRICA boosting infrastruture to attract investment.\" rel=\"nofollow\">Read article<i class=\"dt-icon-the7-arrow-03\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/article><article class=\"post project-odd hidden post-18287 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-home-page-slider category-news category-159 category-39 description-off\" data-name=\"Hon.