-content\">\n\n\t<h3 class=\"entry-title\">\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/courtesy-visit-swedish-parliamentary-delegation\/\" title=\"COURTESY VISIT: SWEDISH PARLIAMENTARY DELEGATION\" rel=\"bookmark\">COURTESY VISIT: SWEDISH PARLIAMENTARY DELEGATION<\/a>\n\t<\/h3>\n\n\t<div class=\"entry-meta\"><span class=\"category-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/home-page-slider\/\" >Home-page Slider<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/category\/news\/\" >News<\/a><\/span><a class=\"author vcard\" href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/author\/p-dumeniparliament-na\/\" title=\"View all posts by \" rel=\"author\">By <span class=\"fn\"><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n\t<div class=\"entry-excerpt\"><p>&nbsp; COURTESY VISIT: SWEDISH PARLIAMENTARY DELEGATION 06 February 2025 The Speaker of the National Assembly, Prof. Peter Katjavivi, received a courtesy visit from a delegation of the Swedish Parliament. Prof. Katjavivi emphasized the strong and cordial relationship between the two countries across various sectors. He described the visit as an opportunity to engage, exchange perspectives,&hellip;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/courtesy-visit-swedish-parliamentary-delegation\/\" class=\"post-details details-type-link\" aria-label=\"Read more about COURTESY VISIT: SWEDISH PARLIAMENTARY DELEGATION\" rel=\"nofollow\">Read article<i class=\"dt-icon-the7-arrow-03\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/article><article class=\"post project-odd hidden post-17636 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-home-page-slider category-news category-159 category-39 description-off\" data-name=\"Speaker of the National Assembly, Hon. Prof. Peter Katjavivi (right) bidding farewell to outgoing KAS Resident Representative, Natalie Russman today.\" data-date=\"\">\n\n<div class=\"post-thumbnail-wrap\">\n\t<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/speaker-o